# Virtual Agent (VA)

Virtual Agent is a conversational interface in ServiceNow that helps users perform tasks through chat.

## Features
- 24/7 self-service support
- Integration with Knowledge Base
- Service Catalog support
- Available on web and mobile
- Integrates with Slack and Microsoft Teams

## Benefits
- Reduces agent workload
- Faster issue resolution
- Improves user experience

## Components
- Topics
- Topic Blocks
- Conversations
- NLU (Natural Language Understanding)
